instant-remote-storage (3.0.0-14) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Avoid duplicate re-uploads after reboot: skip files whose device+inode,
    remote path and SHA-256 are unchanged at cold start. Preserved behavior:
    files deleted and re-added (new inode) or with changed content are
    uploaded again; rename detection unchanged.
  * README.md: clarify MIME-based normalization and tested backends.
  * CONTRIBUTING.md: add minimal contribution guidelines.
  * LICENSE: clarify Expat (MIT) wording (no license change).
  * No change to Standards-Version.

 -- Carlo Capobianchi <bynrflow@gmail.com>  Thu, 11 Sep 2025 17:33:41 +0200

